<section class="section">
  <h2>What We Actually Do</h2>
  <p>We work with diaspora builders to turn ideas into real, operating businesses.</p>
  <p>Not pitch decks. Not theory. <strong>Actual ventures that move goods, serve customers, and generate revenue.</strong></p>

  <p>Our focus sits where culture meets infrastructure:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>food brands and kitchens</li>
    <li>import and distribution systems</li>
    <li>supply chain and logistics operations</li>
    <li>diaspora-led commerce</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>How The Studio Works</h2>
  <p>Berlindisch is the <strong>front-facing venture layer</strong>.</p>
  <p>It brings together ideas, founders, and opportunities from within the network.</p>

  <p>Execution happens through our private partner studio:</p>
  <p><strong><a href="https://bifunctional.xyz" target="_blank">Bifunctional</a></strong>, a design-led venture build system operating as a controlled, high-quality execution layer.</p>

  <p>This separation allows us to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>stay open and collaborative at the ecosystem level</li>
    <li>stay focused and high-quality at the execution level</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <h2>Our Approach</h2>
  <p>Narrative and infrastructure. Identity and distribution. Culture and execution.</p>

  <p>We don’t separate brand, product, and operations.</p>
  <p>Every venture is built as a system, from story to supply chain.</p>
</section>

